==Asaqql (annay) s twallin : ==
iqqand f ufgan ad ur iẓaṛ atrms n tafukt s twallin ns waḥdutnt, acku ɣikad izzḍaṛ ad as iddu iẓṛi ns; g uzmz n utrms n tafukt, ard ttkkant tafukt tugt n wanawn n taḍḍangiwin [[Taliktṛamaɣniṭit|taliktṛamaɣniṭitin]]. Taḍḍangiwin ad gant taḍḍangiwin icqqan f iẓṛi n ufgan, zund ukan :

#'''iẓnẓaṛn n tafukt :''' Aẓnẓṛ n tafukt ur sgis ikṣuḍ ufgan walu f twallin ns, mac ig ur illi utrms afukan; acku g uzmz n utrms afukan ard ttigutn iẓnẓaṛn n tafukt s wakal, ig ggutn iẓnẓaṛn nzzḍaṛn ad ssiḍn tiwallin n ufgan.
#'''iẓnẓaṛn ddu azggaɣ :''' Anaw ad n iẓnẓaṛn ar ittḥṛag aẓṭṭa n tiṭṭ n ufgan.
#'''iẓnẓaṛn nnig inibi :'''  Anaw ad n taḍḍangiwin talikṭṛamaɣniṭitin ihrc ula nttan f twallin n ufgan, acku ar isatti didas tugt n tazḍaṛt, mayad af izzḍaṛ a iḥṛg aẓṭṭa n twallin n ufgan.
